/*

Purpose: Is this anevent on the list of events that this Cams protocol is registered for.
         Suzano Confirmations (CCMS 2346 cnwgb1)

Parameters:			

Return Value: Note that allTrainEventTypes can contain any Event Type not just Train Event Types	

Date		Who		Reason
04 August 2014	cnwgb1	Initial creation PAR 34561 CCMS 2346

*/

vars
begin
   return _camProtocol.allTrainEventTypes.includes(_trans.myEventType);
end;
</source>
